The generated swagger: [Link](https://github.com/Azure/azure-rest-api-specs/blob/82edee201bde3d1de2633221016530141567dd28/specification/devcenter/resource-manager/Microsoft.DevCenter/preview/2025-07-01-preview/devcenter.json#L9780)
```
