```
The actual definition of Sku and the required type that's causing the linter error: [Link](https://github.com/Azure/azure-rest-api-specs/blob/82edee201bde3d1de2633221016530141567dd28/specification/common-types/resource-management/v4/types.json#L470)
```
    "Sku": {
