I am unable to figure out a suppression for this in the readme with a directives ([examples](https://github.com/Azure/azure-rest-api-specs/blob/82edee201bde3d1de2633221016530141567dd28/specification/devcenter/resource-manager/readme.md?plain=1#L43)
